      • columnFor

        public static final AppToFlowColumnPrefix columnFor(String columnPrefix)
        Retrieve an AppToFlowColumnPrefix given a name, or null if there is no match. The following holds true: columnFor(x) == columnFor(y) if and only if x.equals(y) or (x == y == null)
        Parameters:
        columnPrefix - Name of the column to retrieve
        Returns:
        the corresponding AppToFlowColumnPrefix or null

      • columnFor

        public static final AppToFlowColumnPrefix columnFor(AppToFlowColumnFamily columnFamily,
                              String columnPrefix)
        Retrieve an AppToFlowColumnPrefix given a name, or null if there is no match. The following holds true: columnFor(a,x) == columnFor(b,y) if and only if (x == y == null) or a.equals(b) & x.equals(y)
        Parameters:
        columnFamily - The columnFamily for which to retrieve the column.
        columnPrefix - Name of the column to retrieve
        Returns:
        the corresponding AppToFlowColumnPrefix or null if both arguments don't match.
